                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Williamsport</placeName>\n                <date>April 22. 5626</date>.</p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">It was my duty<lb/> to write to you before this and to inform<lb/>\n                you of some particulars resp. congre-<lb/>gationational affairs but there were\n                more<lb/> news to communicate of which I<lb/> could not speak before this time,\n                so<lb/> I had to postpone writing till to-day<lb/> and I hope for this reason you\n                will<lb/> excuse me.</p>\n            <p>You will not be surprised to hear<lb/> that since shortly after my arrival<lb/> at\n                    <hi rend=\"underline\"><placeName>Wmspt</placeName></hi>. I paid my attention to<lb/>\n                <persName>Miss Amelia E. Ulman</persName> because I found<lb/> that all my hopes and\n                imaginations<lb/> were centered in her and was lucky<lb/> enough to gain\n                    <persName>Miss Ulman's</persName> affections<lb/> in return. To-night we are\n                going</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3057dc84/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
